asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Nordica-Drive-Ca-Evo-Womens-Skis-with-EVO-Nsport-Bindings-2013/277237P,default,pd.html  You're not an expert skier but you certainly are not a beginner. The Nordica Drive Ca Evo Skis are designed for you. These skis are known for its Intuitive Profile. That means you'll be riding on a ski that has a very precise and efficient edge transfer that will increase your balance when you're turning. You'll feel more confident when skiing down the blues and will want to venture into the black diamonds. Go for it! The Evo N-Sport Bindings are wider than your average binding which ensures you have more control and balance. Technology and style combine to bring you the Nordica Drive Ca Evo Skis so you can progress out of the intermediate level.
